"use strict";(self.webpackChunkmaria_dot_engineer=self.webpackChunkmaria_dot_engineer||[]).push([[3925],{1875:function(e,o,t){t.r(o),t.d(o,{default:function(){return l}});var n=t(6540),a=t(88),i=t(1042),h=t(4794),s=t(7437);function l(){return(0,s.Y)(n.Fragment,null,(0,s.Y)(i.A,{title:"FAQ"}),(0,s.Y)(a.A,{currentPage:"Coaching",currentSubPage:"FAQ"},(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"What is coaching?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Coaching is a conversation where I ask you questions to help you figure out what you want and how to achieve it. If I have information that would help you, I will ask you for permission to share it, and do so without any expectation that you need to use it. You know what your problems are best, and thus you are the best one to come up with the most appropriate solution for you, I am just here to help you get there. It's like having a good friend who's not afraid to ask the hard and sometimes uncomfortable questions, just that this friend is trained in human psychology and pattern recognition. The ICF, which is the certification body I am part of, defines coaching a bit more formally here:"," ",(0,s.Y)("a",{target:"_blank",href:"https://coachingfederation.org/get-coaching/coaching-for-me/what-is-coaching/"},"what is coaching"),"."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"What type of coaching do you do?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,'My coaching could be described as transformational. Which is coaching speech for "I focus on figuring out what\'s really blocking you and if you even want to do it in the first place, not just surface-level quick fixes." While my goal is to help my clients achieve their goals, and enable them to achieve their dreams, I tend to focus more on the underlying blockers. I believe this will enable my clients to be more self sufficient in the future when they encounter other blockers, than a more surface level, action focused style of coaching.'),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"Do I need coaching?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"No. Nobody needs coaching. That being said, I do believe most people can benefit from coaching."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"Why should I trust you?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"I have over 160 hours of training with Barefoot Coaching Academy, I am a member of the ICF, the leading coaching certification foundation, and I constantly seek to supplement my knowledge through reading as well taking certified courses like the Gottman Relationship Therapy Course."," ",(0,s.Y)(h.Link,{target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer",to:"/coaching/#reviews"},"Here is what some of my past clients said about me.")),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"How much does it cost?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"I charge 90Â£/hour, with different"," ",(0,s.Y)(h.Link,{target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer",to:"/coaching-reinvention/"},"programs")," ","having different costs."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"Where are the coaching sessions held?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Most of my clients are in Europe and the US, as such my coaching sessions are held online via Zoom. After we talk and we agree that we are a good fit, I will send you a link to book them. I have found that even within the same city however some people find it easier to relax and feel safe to discuss certain topics from the safety of their own home over a screen. If you are in Seoul however, I am open to in-person walking coaching."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"How long does each session last?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Most of my sessions last an hour, with walking sessions being one and a half hours."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"So how do I book a call?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"First book a free 30 minute call"," ",(0,s.Y)("a",{target:"_blank",href:"https://cal.com/maria-engineer/30min"},"here")," ","to get to know each other and your goals. During this call I may talk more than during our usual coaching sessions. This call should give you a good idea of whether you could see yourself being coached by me. i.e. if we vibe. If you choose to continue, I will send you a different link for our regular sessions as well as a contract for you to sign for my records."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"What do I need to do to have a good coaching session?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Openness and honesty are the two core values of my coaching. I strive to build a judgement free space so my clients are comfortable honestly sharing parts of themselves they would otherwise keep hidden. That being said, before our session you should have an idea as to what we are going to talk about. After all, how can we achieve a goal if we don't know what that is? Even if the goal is figuring out the goal."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"Why would I want walking coaching?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Coaching while walking is not always applicable, but when the topic is exploration, exploring the outside can help explore our own thought patterns at the same time. Bonus, it is great for the physical body too."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"Will what I tell you make it to anyone?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Everything we talk about is confidential. However if I believe you are in danger to harm yourself or other people, I retain the right to break confidentiality."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"What if I don't think it's working?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"That is ok. I may just not be the right coach for you. Just let me know, and we can end the coaching relationship. If you don't want to end the coaching relationship, we can spend some time together on what specifically is not working and see if there are changes we can make that would help you. If not, we can terminate the coaching relationship. Doesn't mean we have to lose touch completely."),(0,s.Y)("h2",null,"How do I tell you I don't want to continue coaching anymore?"),(0,s.Y)("p",null,"Over email is fine, I know some people wait for their next session to tell their coaches or therapists they don't want to continue, which is just costing them money to terminate a relationship.")))}}}]);
